results.name: NFT.NYC 2023
results.description: NFT.NYC, the leading annual Non-Fungible Token event will return to New York City in 2023 (April 12-14).
results.fullDescription:
Each General Admission Pass is redeemable for a General Admission Ticket to the April 2023 event PLUS:

  • 1 x bonus piece of merch from OpenSea and other NFT.NYC partners.
  • The first 50 General Admission Passes minted will receive an additional General Admission Ticket at no charge.
  • Mints 51-750 have a 1-in-5 chance of receiving a free upgrade from a General Admission Ticket to a VIP Access Ticket.

Each VIP Pass is redeemable for a VIP Access Ticket to the April 2023 event PLUS:

  • 1 x bonus piece of merch from OpenSea and other NFT.NYC partners.
  • The first 50 VIP Passes minted will receive an additional VIP Access Ticket at no charge.
  • Mints 51-250 have a 1-in-5 chance of receiving an additional VIP Access Ticket at no charge.
